      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just reading about the heat death of the universe again... it's hard to even try to care about anything anymore. like, if everything eventually just fades into absolute nothingness and no trace of any human thought or feeling ever remains, what’s even the point of the struggle? it just feels like we're all just elaborate, painful glitches in a system that's heading toward zero. why bother staying in the game when the score is always going to be zero in the end?",
